description.en:
OZAGOLD (OZG): The Coin of reserve Ozalentour.
The aim of OZAGOLD (OZG) is to offer a digital asset that acts as a valuation reserve across 5 liquidity PAIRS : BNB, BUSD, BTC, USDT, ETH
This inflationary Utility Token is used to guarantee the OZP token and to enhance the Ozalentour platform.
